## ✅ Summary of What’s Happening:

| Line                   | Action                        |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| `String.valueOf(half)` | Convert `half` to string      |
| `deleteCharAt(...)`    | Remove last digit from string |
| `reverse()`            | Reverse the shortened string  |
| `s + sb.toString()`    | Form odd-length palindrome    |
| `Long.parseLong(...)`  | Convert back to number        |

